author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how a country has shut down it's Internet and how in a flash of a second you can wake up without being able to reach your loved ones or knowing what's happening. Their are ways to fight back and talk to the people you love even if the Government doesn't want you too. This is how. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: So The Internet Keeps Being Shut Down...
